The positive CD has the following updated information: Punchy, glossy, singles‑driven greatest‑hits: New Wave‑influenced hard rock with anthemic, big choruses, driving electric guitars, layered harmonies and sharp production that lands immediately. Crafted for listeners who prefer instant melodic impact and standalone radio singles over long‑form album flow.

